race.comment: Great betting race to end the day. DUNREAL (3) is a progressive galloper that did more than enough when resuming over 1100m. The step to 1400m looks perfect for his second-up assignment. Pannell goes on and he maps well from the draw. He will be hard to beat. TOTTORI (6) has had three runs back from a long break and might be ready to improve up to 1400m. Suspect he's better than what he's shown so far this spring and want to be with him when he does break through. FULL OF COURAGE (4) was just getting warm at the end of 1200m in a stronger race first-up. He'll strip fitter for this and appreciate the extra furlong. Watch for him finishing over the top of them late. VEXATIOUS CHOICE (8) looks capable of handling the rise in grade and will be going into quaddies and wider plays. Something for the Multiples: PRESS EXPRESS (10) LUDO (15)
